### Week 8 - Backend debugging with REST Client
### Click "Send Request" above each request below.
### (Requires the "REST Client" VS Code extension.)

### 1. Home route  ->  expect "Hello World!"
GET http://localhost:3000

### 2. Get all books  ->  expect a JSON list of 3 books with status 200
GET http://localhost:3000/books

### 3. Add a new book  ->  expect the server to echo back the book you sent
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer",
    "price": 28
}
